{"tid":1540474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人權法點都要pass先可以保障我地！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:44:43.000Z","uid":297973,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"545e2aec0881258a6ed76960909dcc5408035f93","tid":1540474,"uid":297973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"就算政府應承五大訴求都唔可以原諒<br />\n政府同中共幾識講大話大家都知，我地放過政府，轉個頭就被人捉曬啊<br />\n難保以後發生咩事，只有人權法保障到我地<br />\n而且班popo同政府官員一定要受到制裁先對得住被拉被打被非禮被威脅同死者<br />\n如果人權法唔pass，我地三個月黎努力就白費曬la<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3176b308b33b00920ee072d0a474985b368da18","tid":1540474,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"64f39b660ef986750e646f6c26becc4dffe46209","tid":1540474,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n#FiveDemands <br />\n#1down4togo<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"55e86409dfb9dab16d1064d50093b0b70a035f7c","tid":1540474,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"Push!<br />\n同埋撤回逃犯條例放入立會投票, 係幫保皇拉票重建形象!<br />\n<br />\n所以到今日林鄭死咁多人都冇念住真誠撤回"},{"pid":"28e82132f4f4cccce75c44d2ca535be916c81edd","tid":1540474,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"全面抵制藍色餐廳<br />\n一齊打經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvblEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=9fb61be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8N